### Get all studios (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/studios

### Get all studios (custom pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/studios?_page=1&_limit=10

### Get studio by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/studios/3

### Create studio
POST http://localhost:5000/api/studios HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "title": "New studio",
  "location": "Los Angeles",
  "foundation_year": 2024,
  "logo": null,
  "about": null
}

### Update studio
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/studios HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "id": 37,
  "title": "Updated studio",
  "location": "Sydney",
  "foundation_year": 2023,
  "logo": null,
  "about": ""
}

### Patch studio 
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/studios/37 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "title": "Patched studio",
  "location": "Toronto",
  "foundation_year": 1800,
  "about": null
}

### Delete studio
DELETE  http://localhost:5000/api/studios/37 HTTP/1.1
